Introduction
------------
CartoDB Torque App - Creates an animated map visualization from a splunk search with _time, latitude, and longitude fields

Installation
------------
Add the app to your splunk /etc/apps directory

Usage
-----
Enter a search term whose results will contain _time, latitude, and longitude columns.  The app will run an intial search to retreive the time and geo bounds, then initiate a torque animation.  

Use the controls on the right to style the markers on the map.  The app will retain your latest style settings for future use.

